        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer208514170" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer14268950945763100116">Meh. I just could not work up any enthusiasm for this book. The characters fit a little too well into typical romance stereotypes (macho-manly hero, wishy-washy heroine). There was some fun-- I did enjoy the scene where our prim heroine received a makeover from a friendly prostitute-- but my overall impression was blah.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


      <div class="reviewFooter uitext buttons">
          

