        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="liked it"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">liked it</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>

          <span class="greyText">&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;</span>
          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Kindle Edition " href="/book/show/35564946-silver-linings">review of another edition</a>


        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2855034620" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer1226957167203475198">Not her best work. There’s a whole center section where the couple is living in Seattle and NOTHING happens to advance the plot. Her sister’s subplot is entirely inconsequential and does nothing for the storyline. Also, if I’d asked someone to stop calling me “Babe” and they kept doing it all the time, we’d be having a serious talk.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


